Interface NbtWrapper<TType>

  • Type Parameters:

    All Superinterfaces:
    NbtBase<TType>

    public interface NbtWrapper<TType>
extends NbtBase<TType>
    Indicates that this NBT wraps an underlying net.minecraft.server instance.

    Use NbtFactory to load or create instances.
